es a contrast ratio of 4.5:1 for textual elements (i.e. texts), and 3:1 for non-textual elements (i.e. link’s chevron)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However it is higly recommended for mobile devices to reach AAA level because of the screen sizes and luminosity issues, i.e. 7:1 for textual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and 4.5:1 for non-textual elements."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This utility helps to define wether a set of contrast ratio matches AA and AAA or not."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"See for example "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/system.design.orange.com\/0c1af118d\/p\/2531b9-accessibility-compliance","isActive":true}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSFoundations\/documentation\/OUDSFoundations\/OUDSWCAG21Ratio","title":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSWCAG21Ratio"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsfoundations\/oudswcag21ratio"},"ic_layers.png":{"type":"image","identifier":"ic_layers.png","alt":null,"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSFoundations\/ic_layers.png"}]}}}